## Authentication Guard Inventory

| Decorator | Purpose | Checks |
|---|---|---|
| `login_required` | Web UI user session | Session cookie, expiry, account active, org active, force-logout |
| `admin_required` | Super Admin only | All of `login_required` + `role == "super_admin"` |
| `agent_token_required` | Agent API calls | `X-Agent-Token` header or JSON `token` field |

